<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title></title>
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/public/css/styl.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg fixed-top navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/products">CoMeds</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
                    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                        <div class="navbar-nav">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/products/new">Sell on CoMeds</a>
                            <a class="nav-link" href="#abt">About Us</a>
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/users/login">Login</a>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="signout"><svg
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor"
                                    class="bi bi-power" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                    <path d="M7.5 1v7h1V1h-1z" />
                                    <path
                                        d="M3 8.812a4.999 4.999 0 0 1 2.578-4.375l-.485-.874A6 6 0 1 0 11 3.616l-.501.865A5 5 0 1 1 3 8.812z" />
                                </svg> Signout</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-10" style="margin-top: 8%;">
                <div class="card">
                    <h1 class="display-6" style="text-align: center;">Update
                        <%= product.name %>
                    </h1>
                </div>

                <div class="card mt-5">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <form action='/products/<%= product._id %>?_method=PUT' method='POST'>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="name" style="color:white">Name</label><br>

                                <input type="text" name="name" id="name" style="width: 500px;"
                                    value='<%= product.name %>'>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="detail" style="color:white">Detail</label><br>
                                <input type="text" name="detail" style="width: 500px;" id="detail"
                                    value='<%= product.detail %>' />
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="price" style="color:white">Price</label><br>
                                <input type="number" style="width: 500px;" name="price" id="price"
                                    value='<%= product.price %>' />
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="qtyAvl" style="color:white">Quantity</label><br>
                                <input type="number" style="width: 500px;" name="qtyAvl" class="qtyAvl"
                                    value='<%= product.qtyAvl %>' />
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="image" style="color:white">Image</label><br>
                                <input type="text" style="width: 500px;" name="image" class="image"
                                    value='<%= product.image %>' />
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="category" style="color:white">Choose a category: </label><br>
                                <select name="category" id="category">
                                    <% for(let category of categories){ %>
                                        <option value='<%= category %>' <%=product.category===category ? 'selected' : ''
                                            %>><%= category %>
                                        </option>
                                        <% } %>
                                            <option value="medicine">Medicine</option>
                                            <option value="oxygen-cylinder">Oxygen Cylinder</option>
                                            <option value="equipments">Equipments</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer id="abt">
        We are students of IIT (ISM) Dhanbad, who love working with technology. As the second wave of covid hits our
        country, many people are suffering from the shortage of oxygen cylinders and other covid curing medicines.
        Our Web App aimes at providing quick and nearby solutions to those who are suffering. As we all know the changes
        in the world occured during covid period are going to remain for a long haul. So, our Web App will be as useful
        in the post coovid era, as it can be used as a connection between supplier and buyers of medical equipmnent. It
        will remove the barrier of distance between the transacting parties. Itwill aslo help to bring the small scale
        businesses to connect and develop on the internet.
        <hr>
        Contact Us: covidoxymedicals@gmail.com
    </footer>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-JEW9xMcG8R+pH31jmWH6WWP0WintQrMb4s7ZOdauHnUtxwoG2vI5DkLtS3qm9Ekf"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/dummy.js"></script>
</body>

</html>